Read remaining quota / spend across daily, weekly, and monthly windows for the org's resources (`llm_completion`, `ai_rescore`, `web_fetch`). Each entry shows `current_units` vs `max_units` and `resets_at`.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} after a 429 error, to explain to the user which window was hit and when it resets.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} as a pre-flight gate before bulk operations — operations themselves return 429 with hints; this tool is for diagnostics, not gating.
